pedia.org%3APrinciples+for+the+Conservation+of+Heritage+Sites+in+China\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-GCI-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-GCI_4-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-GCI_4-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-GCI_4-2\"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.getty.edu/conservation/field_projects/china/\">\"China Principles\"</a>. Getty Conservation Institute<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">17 February</span> 2011</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=China+Principles&amp;rft.pub=Getty+Conservation+Institute&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.getty.edu%2Fconservation%2Ffield_projects%2Fchina%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APrinciples+for+the+Conservation+of+Heritage+Sites+in+China\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.getty.edu/conservation/publications/pdf_publications/china_prin_2english.pdf\">\"Principles for the Conservation of Heritage Sites in China - Commentary\"</a> <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(PDF)</span>. <a href=\"/wiki/Getty_Conservation_Institute\" title=\"Getty Conservation Institute\">Getty Conservation Institute</a>. pp.&#160;69\u201388<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">17 February</span> 2011</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Principles+for